title: Roasted butternut squash bread
ingredients: ['300g (about 2 medium) roasted butternut squash, mashed', 'olive oil', '14g dried active yeast', '120ml warm water', '235ml milk, warmed slightly', '2 eggs, beaten', '75g butter, melted', '65g brown sugar', 'A pinch of salt', '850g plain flour or bread flour, plus more for kneading']
